1
00:00:00,380 --> 00:00:02,750
Makoto...

2
00:00:03,670 --> 00:00:06,130
You did a great job
with everything I taught you today.

3
00:00:06,130 --> 00:00:08,430
I wanted to give you a round of applause.

4
00:00:08,430 --> 00:00:10,050
Oh, did I?

5
00:00:10,050 --> 00:00:10,970
Yes.

6
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:14,430
Building good relationships with the staff
will bring in more job opportunities.

7
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:17,980
The woman you spoke with today
is an executive at a publishing house.

8
00:00:17,980 --> 00:00:19,980
And if the makeup artist
likes you too,

9
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,020
even more opportunities
will come your way.

10
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:23,360
I must say,

11
00:00:23,820 --> 00:00:26,990
I was surprised when you
went over to talk to him.

12
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:30,820
Well, it's because Yuki was there.

13
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:32,740
He's a friend from college.

14
00:00:32,990 --> 00:00:34,530
Oh, I see.

15
00:00:34,530 --> 00:00:36,700
The assistant?

16
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,750
That explains it.

17
00:00:38,870 --> 00:00:40,960
I should thank him as well.

18
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:43,350
Go ahead and take off your makeup.
We should get ready to leave.

19
00:00:43,630 --> 00:00:44,750
Okay.

20
00:00:52,010 --> 00:00:53,890
Are you two finished?

21
00:00:54,930 --> 00:00:57,390
Yes, I'm done talking with Makoto.

22
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:01,350
But I'd like to have a word with you,

23
00:01:01,810 --> 00:01:03,020
Morimoto-san.

24
00:01:03,310 --> 00:01:04,650
With me?

25
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:09,280
There's something I'd like to ask you.
